01:24:18.550 --> 01:24:21.350 align:middle line:84%
And a system is two or more
things that are connected.

01:24:21.350 --> 01:24:23.870 align:middle line:84%
And they're sending feedback,
circulating information

01:24:23.870 --> 01:24:25.490 align:middle line:90%
