01:24:27.707 --> 01:24:29.290 align:middle line:84%
And the whole becomes,
quote, "greater

01:24:29.290 --> 01:24:30.414 align:middle line:90%
than the sum of its parts."

01:24:30.414 --> 01:24:31.910 align:middle line:84%
Hydrogen and oxygen
come together.

01:24:31.910 --> 01:24:32.710 align:middle line:90%
They're two gases.

01:24:32.710 --> 01:24:34.280 align:middle line:90%
They send, have feedback.

01:24:34.280 --> 01:24:35.980 align:middle line:84%
They circulate energy
and information.

01:24:35.980 --> 01:24:36.780 align:middle line:90%
And what happens?

01:24:36.780 --> 01:24:38.330 align:middle line:84%
